11#ifndef MODULES_AUDIO_CODING_CODECS_ISAC_AUDIO_DECODER_ISAC_T_H_
12#define MODULES_AUDIO_CODING_CODECS_ISAC_AUDIO_DECODER_ISAC_T_H_
13
14#include <vector>
15
16#include "absl/types/optional.h"
17#include "api/audio_codecs/audio_decoder.h"
18#include "api/scoped_refptr.h"
19#include "rtc_base/constructor_magic.h"
20
21namespace webrtc {
22
23template <typename T>
24class AudioDecoderIsacT final : public AudioDecoder {
25 public:
26 struct Config {
27 bool IsOk() const;
28 int sample_rate_hz = 16000;
29 };
30 explicit AudioDecoderIsacT(const Config& config);
31 virtual ~AudioDecoderIsacT() override;
32
33 bool HasDecodePlc() const override;
34 size_t DecodePlc(size_t num_frames, int16_t* decoded) override;
35 void Reset() override;
36 int ErrorCode() override;
37 int SampleRateHz() const override;
38 size_t Channels() const override;
39 int DecodeInternal(const uint8_t* encoded,
40 size_t encoded_len,
41 int sample_rate_hz,
42 int16_t* decoded,
43 SpeechType* speech_type) override;
44
45 private:
46 typename T::instance_type* isac_state_;
47 int sample_rate_hz_;
48
49 RTC_DISALLOW_COPY_AND_ASSIGN(AudioDecoderIsacT);
50};
51
52} // namespace webrtc
53
54#endif // MODULES_AUDIO_CODING_CODECS_ISAC_AUDIO_DECODER_ISAC_T_H_
